# Skills

- Reusable skills — procedures, checklists, and playbooks — live in
  `swarmforge/skills/`. They capture HOW to do recurring work well.
- At the start of a task, scan `swarmforge/skills/README.md`. If a skill's
  "Use when" matches the work at hand, read that skill file and follow it.
- Skills refine execution; they never override the constitution or your role
  prompt. If they ever conflict, the constitution and role prompt win.
- Do not create or modify skills unless the user directs you to.
